Package: paramonte
Type: Package
Title: The Parallel Monte Carlo Library for Monte Carlo simulations
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Shashank Kumbhare <shashank.kumbhare@mavs.uta.edu>
Maintainer: Shashank Kumbhare <shashank.kumbhare@mavs.uta.edu>
Description: 
    ParaMonte is a serial / parallel library of Monte Carlo routines for sampling
    mathematical objective functions of arbitrary-dimensions, in particular,
    the posterior distributions of Bayesian models in data science,
    Machine Learning, and scientific inference.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
